<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Update</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: red;
            color: black;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #e90505;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Password Update</h2>
        <p>Hi <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Use the following link to reset the password of your Avlanche account:</p>
        <p><a href="https://avlanche.onrender.com/users/reset-password/<%= user.accessToken %>" class="button">Reset
                Password</a></p>
        <p>Or paste the given link in your browser:</p>
        <p>https://avlanche.onrender.com/users/reset-password/<%= user.accessToken %>
        </p>
        <p>Thanks & regards from Team Avlanche!</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>